{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779250856186,"sessionID":"ses_1bc6319d2ffe3a4fAFqTlgq0bZ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_00_XeOJChpZ2DcA2335xsSI2649","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/index.yaml"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/index.yaml</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: id: US-INDEX\n2: role: all\n3: feature: Splash screen with automatic redirect to property search\n4: page: index.html\n5: goal: |\n6:   A visitor landing on the NestFind splash screen sees the brand logo and tagline\n7:   before being automatically redirected to the property search page.\n8: \n9: acceptance_criteria:\n10:   - id: AC-1\n11:     description: Splash screen displays the NestFind logo, tagline \"Finding your way home\", and a loading indicator\n12:     ui_route: /\n13:     endpoint: none\n14:     expected: \"NestFind logo visible, tagline text visible, loading bar animation runs, 200 OK\"\n15:   - id: AC-2\n16:     description: After ~2 seconds, the browser auto-redirects to the property search home page\n17:     ui_route: /\n18:     endpoint: none\n19:     expected: \"URL changes to /05-home.html (or equivalent /home route) after splash timeout\"\n20: \n21: boundary_cases:\n22:   - case: \"Slow network — splash screen remains visible beyond 2 seconds; loading indicator animates continuously until redirect fires\"\n23:   - case: \"JavaScript disabled — splash screen stays static; no redirect occurs; essential for graceful fallback\"\n24: \n25: error_scenarios:\n26:   - scenario: \"Redirect target (/05-home.html) returns 404 — browser shows 404 page after timeout instead of property search\"\n27:   - scenario: \"Network failure during splash — splash page stays visible until timeout then navigates to unreachable target\"\n28: \n29: state_transitions:\n30:   - state: loading\n31:     expected: \"Animated loading bar at bottom of splash screen\"\n32:   - state: ready\n33:     expected: \"Auto-redirect fires; browser navigates to property search page\"\n34: \n35: fixture_refs:\n36:   - none\n\n(End of file - total 36 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"id: US-INDEX\nrole: all\nfeature: Splash screen with automatic redirect to property search\npage: index.html\ngoal: |\n  A visitor landing on the NestFind splash screen sees the brand logo and tagline\n  before being automatically redirected to the property search page.\n\nacceptance_criteria:\n  - id: AC-1\n    description: Splash screen displays the NestFind logo, tagline \"Finding your way home\", and a loading indicator\n    ui_route: /\n    endpoint: none\n    expected: \"NestFind logo visible, tagline text visible, loading bar animation runs, 200 OK\"\n  - id: AC-2\n    description: After ~2 seconds, the browser auto-redirects to the property search home page\n    ui_route: /\n    endpoint: none\n    expected: \"URL changes to /05-home.html (or equivalent /home route) after splash timeout\"\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/user_stories/index.yaml","time":{"start":1779250855864,"end":1779250856185}},"id":"prt_e439d7a56001rTurM4LFEX21Of","sessionID":"ses_1bc6319d2ffe3a4fAFqTlgq0bZ","messageID":"msg_e439d2a2d0015cjPuHT5MUYonP"}}
